All global variable names. Add a prefix to all variable names that you declare outside a function scope. <p>While prefixing, please remember that refixes should consist of either your <code>themename_</code>, <code>authorname_</code>, or <code>frameworkname_</code></p><p><em>Example</em></p><p>```php
$mythemename_variable = "whatever";</p><p>function name mythemename_whatever(){
    //your function body goes here
}</p><p>add_action( 'after_setup_theme', 'mythemename_setup' );</p><p>function mythemename_setup(){
    add_image_size("mythemename_single_hero", 1140, 9999);
    //rest
}
```</p>
